name: Skull High
description:
A platforming video game themed around Halloween created by Alex Benishek, Sofia Carrillo, and Alex Kautz. The goal of the game is to move your player, a skull, high above the sky by jumping on rock platforms. The skull has a health bar that decreases as time passes by. You can increase your health throughout the game by grabbing smiley potatoes and the more rare but more valuable fries.

Can you make it all the way up to the Big Burger and win it all?

You can also play the game online here: https://alexbenishek.com/sky-high/sky-high.html
